+
+## P0 – do first (security + high ROI)
+1. Artifact signature/hash verification in update flow.
+2. Single URL opening policy and scheme allowlist.
+3. Replace `GlobalScope` usage in update restart path.
+4. Add `PortableStore` + route settings access through it.
+
